OL,3,CMPs write to M&S and Co-op as ITV News
OL,4,Clearns new details of cyberattack
OL,6,FAttempted attacks against Harrods
OL,7,Ffollow similar cyberattacks against
OL,8,FM&S and The Co-op, as ITV News'
OL,9,FBusiness Editor Joel Hills reports.
OL,11,FThe chair of the Business and Trade
OL,12,FSelect Committee is writing to the
OL,13,Fbosses of Marks and Spencer and The Co-
OL,14,Fop, to express concern about
OL,15,Fcyberattacks faced by both retailers.
OL,17,FIt comes as ITV News has learnt the
OL,18,Fhacking has disrupted loyalty cards,
OL,19,Fhandheld scanners and apps used to
OL,20,Freport security incidents in M&S
OL,21,Fstores.
