OL,3,CMPs write to M&S and Co-op as ITV News
OL,4,Clearns new details of cyberattack
OL,6,FMPs are seeking reassurance that the
OL,7,Fcompanies are managing the incidents
OL,8,Feffectively, and getting adequate
OL,9,Fsupport from GCHQ and other agencies.
OL,11,FThe parliamentary committee also wants
OL,12,Fclarity on whether IT systems across
OL,13,Fthe UK retail sector are sufficiently
OL,14,Frobust, and whether ransomeware hacks
OL,15,Fare becoming more frequent and
OL,16,Fsuccessful.
OL,18,FAt M&S, online and app orders are down
OL,19,Ffor a seventh consecutive day.
