OL,6,FITV News understands that its stores
OL,7,Fare still facing these issues:
OL,9,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,10,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,11,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,12,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,14,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for M&S
OL,15,Fsaid: "Our stores are open and we are
OL,16,Fcontinuing to serve our customers. As
OL,17,Fpart of our proactive management of
OL,18,Fthe incident, we took a decision to
OL,19,Ftake some of our systems temporarily
OL,20,Foffline."
