OL,6,FMeanwhile, The Co-op has told staff
OL,7,Fthey can no longer access the
OL,8,Fcompany's IT system remotely from
OL,9,Fhome, following an attempted hack at
OL,10,Fthe weekend.
OL,12,FThe company has shut down some of its
OL,13,Fback office and call centre services,
OL,14,Fbut that all of its 2,000 stores and
OL,15,F800 funeral homes are "trading as
OL,16,Fnormal".
